{"tid":1356741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣要人, 有資源] 我地要出師有名，用文宣保留民意!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:00:08.000Z","uid":8762,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ef950ecf71d75bd2b02190cf02fc1a479a0949","tid":1356741,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">懶人包:<br />\n我地極需要文宣搶返民意，下面有圖請你幫幫手share或者印出黎放上連儂牆，有TG GP可以加入幫手俾意見/收集/出圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d90498550756c68d1fd66654d463ebdb1276fd2","tid":1356741,"uid":176731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b06a3402a41ebc3ac300d13e423422591e8614c0","tid":1356741,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得<br />\n１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動</span></span>"},{"pid":"1add8edd8cc6271a502ef4b0bc194753125624e2","tid":1356741,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b5dd0d20282ffdf321976f08538fb34b8408ad","tid":1356741,"uid":101903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"[推post]<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再入去個啲膠POST分化POST批鬥POST同FAKE NEWS屌鬼住，阻到正經POST，理返正經野先啦<br />\n黑警無預警丟煙開槍打手足開撚左三十幾槍呀！<br />\n堆仆街黑社會見人就打呀！仲有仆街黑警照住呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">覆POST之前諗真啲先！<br />\n獨立思考！唔好完全盡信正負評！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！<br />\n爭取五大訴求！</span></span></strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">1. 全面撤回送中條例\n2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究\n4. 全面實行雙普選\n5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲</code></pre><br />\n[/推post]"},{"pid":"b3157c05ea241f74cea1b263dad88f5124ce9ddc","tid":1356741,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f74a5196ff315dee4f21e7e3ff24162d04060be","tid":1356741,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保衛元朗，不要警黑"},{"pid":"9da193b2b6de847f4410a1f6d9b34e9ad4ab06a3","tid":1356741,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"警察信唔過，唯有靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121d6ecd0b94ae879a35ebda28d0f199df291ca","tid":1356741,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63rM8Kp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63rM8Kp.jpg&h=e207bf3e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n想問係上環比槍射中頭個位義士宜加點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59c65fcd712b73f839e4ab758eea48472fcdf4d","tid":1356741,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6661b0a04bf83a9ce6ea638e5394bff9ff9a27d3","tid":1356741,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b8c3c3f1f038700ce0365e987ec3c55cebb72c0","tid":1356741,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d121d6ecd0b94ae879a35ebda28d0f199df291ca","tid":1356741,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63rM8K